name: Zhuzhong Qian
content: Zhuzhong Qian Zhuzhong Qian PhD, Professor Follow Nanjing,China Nanjing University Email Google Scholar Short Biography Dr. Qian received Ph.D. degree in computer science from Nanjing University (NJU) in 2007. He is currently a full professor in the School of Computer Science, Nanjing University. He is also a research fellow of the State Key Laboratory for Novel Software Technology. Research Interest My current research interests include but not limit to: Inference Acceleration for LLM Edge AI Cloud Computing Distributed AI Systems Correspondence Email: qzz@nju.edu.cn Office: Computer Science Building 617, Nanjing University Xianlin Campus Postal Address: 210023
